  "title": "Trader",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Seek new business opportunities globally and work as a team to develop new accounts</li><li>Interact with traders and handle negotiations of both parties (seller and buyer) concerned</li><li>Develop new markets and close cooperation with Business Development and other Trading desks</li><li>Assist to develop hedging strategies to lock in profitable physical trades and contribute to the management of the team’s paper positions</li><li>Ensure proper execution of trades (physical and paper)</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree in Business/Commercial</li><li>Minimum 3 years of trading experience</li><li>Self-motivated & has the passion to work in a fast-paced and dynamic environment</li><li>Possess extensive industry relationships and customer resources</li><li>Good knowledge in statistics, currencies, derivatives, and financial      instruments</li><li>Strong growth Mindset with Entrepreneurial spirit; Self-Starter</li><li>Experience in all commodities will be considered</li></ul>",
